{"tid":1309722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[科大學生會反送中支援基金 月結財政報告]","createTime":"2019-07-12T10:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T00:27:51.000Z","uid":77867,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3fd35b7b99586a715ade1846113410d9d0fb9403","tid":1309722,"uid":77867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:29:23.000Z","msg":"[科大學生會反送中支援基金 月結財政報告]<br />\n<br />\n本會於六月十一日通過撥款一百零三萬港元作反送中支援基金，以下為截至七月十日基金所批出之所有*款項，總額為港元十萬零九千一百五十四元六毫。歡迎各界人士向本會查詢及監察該款項去向。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;HKUST Students&rsquo; Union Anti China Extradition Support Fund Monthly Financial Report&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nThe Students' Union has approved the allocation of 1,030,000 Hong Kong Dollars as Anti China Extradition Support Fund on June 11th. Total* grant approved by the Support Fund as of July 10th is attached bellow. Current grant amount is 109,154.6 Hong Kong Dollars. The Union welcomes enquiry and supervision from all parties regarding the Support Fund.<br />\n<br />\n本會查詢電郵地址：<br />\nStudents' Union enquiry email address:<br />\nsu_union@ust.hk<br />\n<br />\n*不包括予立場新聞捐款<br />\n*Donation to Stand News excluded<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jmPdOq3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjmPdOq3.png&h=604b33c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pOYRz54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpOYRz54.png&h=5dfb822e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07238c55cdf98456aef789e95a27523814944e9d","tid":1309722,"uid":274310,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:30:41.000Z","msg":"都唔少 科大出錢出力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956b9c7dcde8be3258f338d0afce4144f914397e","tid":1309722,"uid":201687,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:32:41.000Z","msg":"原來保護設備都唔少"},{"pid":"d020a6c922755aa7181654245f46bcdef176e2